description: This header file declares internal functions for the Slap Bmc2 Server Object used in Service Logic Aggregation Plane (SLAP) implementation. It includes function prototypes for resetting the server object and executing or transferring pages, indicating it is part of the server's internal API definitions.

methods.name: SlapBmc2SrvoReset
methods.description: Resets the Slap Bmc2 Server Object to its initial state.

methods.name: SlapBmc2SrvoExecute
methods.description: Executes a page based on the provided page path.

methods.name: SlapBmc2SrvoTransfer
methods.description: Transfers a page based on the provided page path.
